    public class TranslateMessageLayout<E>
extends ch.qos.logback.classic.PatternLayout
implements ch.qos.logback.core.Layout<ch.qos.logback.classic.spi.ILoggingEvent>
    Extends PatternLayout in order to keep logging pattern feature while trying to translate message at the same time. In case that messageService bean is not available (ie. spring context is not loaded yet) or that message key is not found, message will be logged untranslated.
